It may not matter that much since story was still delivered all the same but I just don't see any reasons for the TLers to go this far. Heres's a just some of the changes: (p39) MC: "Would you please stop? Im actually very troubled here. In the first place, Were really this kind kind of person, Mrs .Ichinose?" Wife: "Did you think I'm a diligent vice president? [TLer added a lot of extras stuff]", (p39-40 bottom dialogue to next page) What wife was saying was "Actually... Every...single...day... I masturbate.". There are more misTLs but I think the biggest one is (p57). Wife asks if MC minds doing it with a married woman, and man actually said "I- I don't think we should do this" But it was translated into the opposite of what he said. Again, the story is all the same but the dialogues were played around by the TLers a lot. Just informing you guys that.
